description.plain: Simon Henner, known professionally as French 79, is a French electronic music artist from Marseille, France. His music career began in 2010 with founding Nasser, in which he was a guitarist. After releasing 4 albums, he created a pop group, Husbands, along with fellow French artists Kid Francesoli (Mathieu Hocine) and Oh! Tiger Mountain (Mathieu Poulain). He first produced music under the French 79 name in 2014 with his debut single “Between the Buttons” and EP Angel.

body.plain: Simon Henner, known professionally as French 79, is a French electronic music artist from Marseille, France. His music career began in 2010 with founding Nasser, in which he was a guitarist. After releasing 4 albums, he created a pop group, Husbands, along with fellow French artists Kid Francesoli (Mathieu Hocine) and Oh! Tiger Mountain (Mathieu Poulain). He first produced music under the French 79 name in 2014 with his debut single “Between the Buttons” and EP Angel.

description.plain: “‘Hometown’ is one of my most successful tracks in the sense that it’s the first one where I expose myself by singing and writing about myself,” Henner tells Billboard Dance. “I’m talking about my hometown, Epinal, where I grew up, built myself, started making music, skateboarding, spent my teenage and built my own personality. It is also a track built in two parts with a long intro that reveals the melody and harmonies, plus a second part that’s more rhythmic. This is the two parts of French 79 universe: harmonies and melodies on the one hand and dance floor on the other.”

songs.title: By Your Side
songs.lyrics:
You’re my best friend
And that will never change
I’ll come pick you up
Then get you high
And ride every wave
We’ll sing our favorite songs
Till the sun begins to rise
Forget all about
People throwing shade
And the games that they play

[x2]
I will find a way
To always be there (to always be there)
And I will be brave
You don’t have to be scared
With me by your side (by your side)

(I know)
Can you feel the beat?
Turn up the high energy
You know it’s true
There’s nothing we can’t do
When we realize our dreams

After all we been through
I could never let you down
Just take my hand
Let's laugh and lets dance
With the ones we love

(I will always be there)
(You don't have to be scared)
(With me by your side)

[x2]
I will find a way
To always be there (to always be there)
And I will be brave
You don’t have to be scared
With me by your side (by your side)
